FBIS4-57254 "drlat095_m_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-095 Daily Report 16 May 1994 Brazil Orestes Quercia Nominated PMDB Presidential Candidate Orestes Quercia Nominated PMDB Presidential Candidate PY1605132294 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network in Portuguese 1000 GMT 16 May 94 PY1605132294 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network Portuguese BFN [Excerpt] Orestes Quercia has been nominated presidential candidate for the PMDB [Brazilian Democratic Movement Party]. Quercia defeated former Parana Governor Roberto Requiao in the party internal elections held throughout the country on 15 May. Quercia won the internal PMDB elections by a broad margin. PMDB President Luiz Henrique said that despite the high rate of abstentions, he believes that the result reflects the will of the PMDB grassroots. [passage omitted]
